3. The Roadmap doesn't seem farfetched 

There are A LOT of projects in this space that are sharing so many buzzwords in their white paper about what they will do but in reality things promised will take years. 

This project has a believable timeline and team for execution.

Normally when NFT projects say that are "creating a game" they have never done so before and don't have anyone on the team that can execute. 

The studio behind this project actually has done so in the past and let you see their work.
